## Ajouter le repo bitnami
```bash
helm repo add bitnami https://charts.bitnami.com/bitnami 
```
## Installer la chart postgres
```bash
helm install postgres bitnami/postgresql --namespace motower-ihm --version "12.11.1" -f values.yaml
```
## Supprimer la chart postgres
```bash
helm uninstall postgres  --namespace motower-ihm 
```
## Verifier les PVC de la chart
```bash
kubectl get pvc -n motower-ihm
```
## Supprimer le PVC de la chart
```bash
kubectl delete pvc/data-postgres-postgresql-0 -n motower-ihm
```